LYNCH
v.
WOMBLE, Carlyle. No. 345P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 18, 2005. Richard L. Rainey, Charlotte, for Womble, Carlyle, Sandridge & Rice.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 23rd day of June 2005 by Plaintiff for "Notice of Appeal":

"Motion Dismissed ex mero motu by order of the Court in conference this the 18th day of August 2005."
